## Planned Upgrades (In Progress)
1. **LLM upgrade** — Qwen2.5 14B or Mistral 7B on GPU server (change model path + add n_gpu_layers=-1)
2. **Translation** — Replace Sarvam Translate with IndicTrans2 (AI4Bharat, open source, GPU server)
3. **Image upscaling** — Add Real-ESRGAN as /upscale_image endpoint on GPU server
4. **Zoro avatar video** — HeyGen Talking Photo API (New_Zoro.png + Sarvam audio → talking video)
5. **Video caching** — Cache by slide_id + language key, serve from /videos/{filename}

